text: The Swan 40 Frers was designed by German Frers and built by Nautor's Swan and first launched in 1992 it is the second Swan 40 model produced. ==References== ==External links== * Nautor Swan * German Frers Official Website Category:Sailing yachts Category:Keelboats Category:1990s sailboat type designs Category:Sailboat types built by Nautor Swan Category:Sailboat type designs by Germán Frers
